    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she's been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of adventures left to give. I've taken great care of it, and it still drives like a dream\u2014perfect for anyone who wants a reliable, comfy car without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019m so excited for someone else to enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
