    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained 2017 Porsche Macan S in a sophisticated Volcano Grey Metallic. This vehicle has been driven with care and presents in impressive condition for its mileage. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear passenger door. The interior is a smoke-free environment featuring black premium leather; the seats are firm and comfortable, with only light creasing on the driver-side bolster consistent with regular use. All technological features, including the navigation system, heated seats, and the panoramic roof, are fully operational. Mechanically, this Macan S is robust. It comes with a complete service history, having recently received an oil change and a fresh set of filters. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. There are no leaks, no warning lights on the dash, and the transmission shifts smoothly through every gear. This is a reliable, high-performance SUV that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and utility.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
